    • run

      public Optional<ExtractedGpxResult> run(File file, Path outputFolder)
      Description copied from interface: GpxFileRunner
      This method will be called on every GPX file encountered. If everything works properly, it will be turned into a image map. Metadata about the GPX file are also extracted and stored in a map.
      Specified by:
      run in interface GpxFileRunner
      Parameters:
      file - input GPX file
      outputFolder - a path that can be used as an output folder
      Returns:
      a map containing the GPX metadata, an empty Optional if something went wrong
